      <title>Opinion: Remembering Sandra Grimes, mole hunter</title>
      <author>Scott Simon</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/08/09/nx-s1-5490973/opinion-remembering-sandra-grimes-mole-hunter</link>
