      <title>During an 'Island Storm,' two kids on an adventure ask — 'Do we try for more?'</title>
      <author>Samantha Balaban</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/08/09/nx-s1-5485308/picture-this-island-storm-brian-floca-sydney-smith</link>
      <comments>https://text.npr.org/2025/08/09/nx-s1-5485308/picture-this-island-storm-brian-floca-sydney-smith</comments>
